# Adding Blogs & Changelogs

## Blog (SQL-first — website + mobile)

Write **both** Supabase keys:

1. `app_config.blog` — listing card metadata
2. `app_config.blog_marketing_bodies` — `{ "slug": "# Title\n\nmarkdown..." }`

Generate SQL: `node scripts/generate-blog-sql.mjs post.json` — see `frontend/docs/BLOG_SQL_PUBLISH.md`.

Also: Admin → Blog (Save), Marketing Radar → Publish to blog.

Shared module: `lib/blog/publishBlogPost.ts`. Reader: `getDbBlogPost()` in `lib/blog/dynamicBlogPosts.ts`.

**Do not** add new posts to `blog-defaults.ts` / `blogContent` unless explicitly asked.

## Changelog

- `app_config` key `changelog` via SQL migration
- Template: `085_changelog_and_blog_march_2025.sql`

